snippet.title: Card Shark | Available June 2 on PC & Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Coming June 2 for PC & Nintendo Switch | Demo on Both
Preorder Now: https://cardsharkgame.com

Card Shark is an adventure game full of cunning, intrigue, and delectable deceit. Enter a world where you’ll need to play your opponents better than you play your cards.
